   288	### `reference/compose/.env.example`
   289	
   290	Plain dotenv. Comments document each value. Ships dev-only secrets:
   291	
   292	```dotenv
   293	# EDEN reference Compose stack — example environment.
   294	# Copy to ".env" for local use; "compose up" reads from .env automatically.
   295	# CI uses these defaults verbatim; do NOT use these in production.
   296	
   297	# --- Postgres ---
   298	POSTGRES_DB=eden
   299	POSTGRES_USER=eden
   300	POSTGRES_PASSWORD=eden-dev-password-change-me
   301	POSTGRES_HOST_PORT=5433
   302	
   303	# --- Gitea ---
   304	# SECRET_KEY: gitea uses this for cookie / CSRF / 2FA encryption.
   305	# Generate with: gitea generate secret SECRET_KEY  (or 64 hex chars).
   306	GITEA_SECRET_KEY=0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcd
   307	# INTERNAL_TOKEN: gitea uses this for inter-component auth.
   308	GITEA_INTERNAL_TOKEN=0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcd
   309	GITEA_HOST_PORT=3001
   310	GITEA_SSH_HOST_PORT=2222
   311	```
